'''Afella''' is a Mountain located in the Western '''High-Atlas''' range. Its highest peak is at 4043 metres.<ref>[http://www.madteam.net/rutas/alpinismo/especial-atlas--macizo-del-toubkal-7.madteam].'Afella (Spanish)''.</ref><ref>[https://www.happyknowledge.com/post/Le%20bisounours/VNkFVo9a_Qg2JAuw].'Afella (French)''.</ref>

